-# Breadcrumbs and Explore button
%section#header_toolbar.container-fluid
  .container
    #breadcrumbs
      %ul
        %li= link_to "Home", "/"
        %li 
          %span Terms of Use
    = render "partials/explore_dropdown"



-# Main Talk content
%section.container#main_content

  #page_header
    #page_title.left
      %h1 Terms of Use
    = render "partials/share"
    
  -# Left column, main content: About Us information
  .box.double.left

    .column_row#about_description
      .column.column_double
        %p This website is provided as a public service to share ideas, inspire action, and ignite change to positively impact our world. We welcome anyone willing to join us in this effort. You are encouraged to view as many CIW Talks as you wish for free, and to share what inspires your with others both online and offline.
        
        %p Anyone can join the Chicago Ideas Week Community and share the content and ideas found on the site. To join, you must provide your name and valid email address. When posting please consider that you are speaking to a wide and public audience. We encourage thought-provoking, inspiring and clever discourse. In short, show respect for all users and people featured on the site.

        %p Please respect the law. Do not post copyrighted material (unless you own the copyright) or attempt to engage in illegal behavior of any sort.

        %p CIW reserves the right to remove any comments or content from the site, for any reason and without prior warning.

        %p If you violate these terms, or otherwise act disrespectfully, disruptively or illegally on chicagoideas.com, we reserve the right to terminate your membership, at any time, and without prior warning.

        %p Welcome to Chicago Ideas Week, and start turning your ideas into action!



  -# Include Sidebar Items
  #sidebar
    = render "partials/sponsors"
    = render "partials/social"
    = render "partials/newsletter_form"